      "bgName": "env_photo_studio-00-000-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――新曲MV撮影の現場にて",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "この曲に合った表情やポーズ……ですか\n分かりましたわ。それではこういった感じはいかが？",
      "startTime": 7.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "（琴乃ったら、戻って来たと思えばすぐに目覚ましい）\n（活躍をして……やはりあなたは、凄いですわね）",
      "startTime": 18.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "（ですが、私も負けるつもりはさらさらありませんから）\n（油断していたらいつでもセンターの座を奪いますわよ）",
      "startTime": 28.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（すず……力強くて、それでいて優しい表情をしてる）\n（こんな顔をするようになったんだな……）",
      "startTime": 39.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "（これからは、私が今までの何倍も、何十倍も）\n（しっかりと月ストを支えてみせますわ）",
      "startTime": 47.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "（あなたが照らしてくれたように。私も、あなたを）\n（照らします。もう、一人で迷わないように）",
      "startTime": 55.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "（私達五人の月のテンペストで）\n（アイドルの頂点に輝きますわよ！）",
      "startTime": 64.2666674296,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-night.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-night"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――MV撮影から数日後",
      "startTime": 68.3666707629,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\n今度の単独ライブでのセンターについてですが……",
      "startTime": 72.1000007629,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "練習で私と琴乃がそれぞれセンターに立った時の\n手応えを比べた上で、メンバーで話し合いをしましたわ",
      "startTime": 79.6333340962,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "結果はどうだったんだ？",
      "startTime": 84.1666722933,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "センターは、どちらか一方が務めるのではなく\n曲ごとに切り替えることにしましたの",
      "startTime": 90.1333340962,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "そしてその結果……この間話していた曲のセンターは\nこの私が務めることになりましたわ！",
      "startTime": 98.2333340962,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "ふっふーん。やはり私こそが\nあの曲のセンターにふさわしいんですのよ！",
      "startTime": 105.1333340962,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "みんな納得した上で、すずが人一倍思い入れのある曲の\nセンターになれて良かったよ。おめでとう",
      "startTime": 112.7333340962,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "後はもう、単独ライブに向けてステージングを\nひたすら詰めていくだけですわ",
      "startTime": 119.4286859194,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "成宮家の親族一同も感動でむせび泣くパフォーマンスを\n見せて差し上げますわよ！",
      "startTime": 127.1666674296,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――月スト単独ライブ当日",
      "startTime": 130.073543167,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "みなさん、私達月ストの単独ライブ……\n楽しんでいますか？",
      "startTime": 136.7000007629,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 5266.645526899993,
          "startTime": 137.8333340962
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz015.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ、ありがとうございます\nみなさんの熱気がこちらまで伝わってきますわ",
      "startTime": 142.3999946593,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz016.m4a",
      "text": "さて、次の曲なんですが\nこの曲は琴乃が月ストを離れていた頃",
      "startTime": 150.366661326,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz017.m4a",
      "text": "……私達が四人体制の時に作った曲ですの",
      "startTime": 154.5666824657,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz018.m4a",
      "text": "もう、琴乃ったら。そんな神妙な面持ちにならないで\nくださいまし。どーんと構えていなさい？",
      "startTime": 163.0999946593,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_laugh-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7233.318297199986,
          "startTime": 166.0000007629
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz019.m4a",
      "text": "四人で新曲を作るとなった時、初めは難航しましたわ\nいろいろなことがあり過ぎて",
      "startTime": 172.4999916075,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz020.m4a",
      "text": "いろいろな想いが溢れ過ぎて……\n気持ちが、言葉が、まとまりませんでしたの",
      "startTime": 178.4275637625,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz021.m4a",
      "text": "でも、私達が今一番考えていることは何か……\nと考えたら、答えは一つでした",
      "startTime": 188.9999916075,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz022.m4a",
      "text": "テーマが決まればとんとん拍子で、曲が完成するまで\nあまりに早くて、思わず笑ってしまいましたわね",
      "startTime": 196.4999966937,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（すずのMCにみんなが引き込まれてる）\n（ファンも気になっていた話題なんだろうな）",
      "startTime": 204.466673533,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz023.m4a",
      "text": "初めてこの曲を披露した時、私達は\n「この想いが届けばいいな」と願って歌いました",
      "startTime": 212.1999966937,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz024.m4a",
      "text": "結果として、月ストは五人に戻ることが出来て\nBIG4にもなれましたわ",
      "startTime": 221.1666633604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz025.m4a",
      "text": "でも……私、思いましたの",
      "startTime": 223.5333511668,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3"
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_10_03-suz026.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルとして輝かしい栄光を手にしたことよりも\n私達が……ふたたび五人揃ったことの方が嬉しい",
      "startTime": 232.6333300271,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_flowerstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s3"
